        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "GOD OF GOODNESS, we give thanks\nfor the gift of life, wonder beyond words;\nfor the awareness of soul, our light within;\nfor the world around us, so filled with beauty;\nfor the richness of the earth, which day by day sustains us;\nfor all these and more, we offer thanks.\nבָּרוּךְ אַתָּה, יְיָ, הַטוֹב שִׁמְךְ וּלְךָ נָאֶה לְהוֹדוֹת.\nBaruch atah, Adonai, hatov shimcha ul'cha na-eh l'hodot.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-17T16:48:24.593Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "SjPyeBFjKJVJ_c1KT7Pf"
